714805f-a.title: Manhattan: 91st Street - 2nd Avenue
714805f-a.text:
91st Street, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of Second
Avenue.
September 3, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

714806f-a.title: Manhattan: 91st Street - 2nd Avenue
714806f-a.text:
91st Street, north side, from Second to Third Avenues, inclusive.
In the foreground are buildings occupied by the George Ehret Hell
Gate Brewery; in the background are the Jacob Ruppert and George
Ringler Breweries.
February 2, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

714807f-a.title: Manhattan: 91st Street - 2nd Avenue
714807f-a.text:
91st Street, south side, from, but not including, Second
to Third Avenues.
February 2, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

714808f-a.title: Manhattan: 91st Street - 2nd Avenue
714808f-a.text:
91st Street, north side, from Second to Third Avenues, showing
the Ehret, Ruppert and Ringler brewery buildings, as seen over
the roofs on the south side of the street.
September 3, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
